###TA EHW KAI STO TETRADIO


-Ti einai ta enzyma?
Einai makromoria, prwteinika synh8ws pou droun ws biologikoi katalytes pou epitaxynoun megales xhmikes antidraseis.

Yparxoyn 75.000 enzyma ston an8rwpo.

Kathe enzymo leitourgei gia mia xhmikh antidrash.

-Ta enzyma katalyoun antidraseis:
(1) meiwnontas thn energeia energopoihshs twn antidrwntwn.
(Energeia energopoihshs = h energeia pou xreiazetai gia na antidrasoun ta antidronta metajy tous)
(2) prosanatolizontas katallhla ta antidrwnta.


Kathe enzymo exei ena energo kentro pou koumponoun ta moria-ypostrwmata(antidrwnta) epanw tou opws ena kleidi se kleidaria,
sth synexeia molis koumpwsoun katalhgei se enzymo-ypostrwmata ta opoia sto telos dhmiourgoun nea proionta.

---Idiothtes Enzymwn---

(1) H katalytikh drash tous ka8orizetai apo thn tritotagh/tetartotagh domh.
(2) Droun poly grhgora.
(3) Den symmetexoun sthn antidrash poy katalyoun (paramenoun analloiwta & mporoun na xrhsimopoih8oun jana).
(4) Exoun ypshlh ejeidikeush (1 enzymo -> 1 xhmikh antidrash).
(5) H drastikothta tous ephreazetai apo th 8ermokrasia & to pH (metousiwsh).

*Epipleon*
Den einai ola ta Enzyma prwteines. Ta enzyma auta onomazontai rivoenzyma kai einai Enzyma RNA.
-Leitourgies sxetikes me apokoph eswniwn apo mRNA, dhmiourgia peptidikwn desmwn...
